-- Onyx CEO to retire next year
-- 
-- Thu Oct 4, 2007 7:36am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/04/us-onyxpharmaceuticals-management-idUSWNAS553020071004

 

 (Reuters) - Onyx Pharmaceuticals Inc ONXX.O said its Chief Executive Hollings Renton plans to retire next year 

 Emeryville, California-based Onyx said Renton would remain chairman of the board. The company said it is initiating a search for a successor. (Reporting by Shamik Paul in Bangalore)